## About This Analysis {background-color="#1a1a2e"}

::: {.incremental}
- **Client:** Trauma Resource Institute (TRI) — a nonprofit offering trauma-informed training
- **Data:** 28 days of GA4 event-level data (~3,700 sessions)
- **Goal:** Understand what drives users from a page view to a booking conversion
- **Tools:** R · Quarto · ggplot2 · plotly · GA4
:::

---

## Research Question {background-color="#2F80ED" color="white"}

> **Do users who view more pages convert at higher rates?**  
> And which traffic sources and devices drive the most engaged visitors?

